data.description: This 3-bed, 2-bath log cabin is nestled on a lush treed lot that offers stunning views of Little Bear Creek Reservoir. It boasts rustic charm with a covered porch, 14x16 deck, open floor plan, and fireplace. It features a kitchen with stainless steel appliances and charming bedrooms. Descending the bluff, a hidden gem awaits - a small, secluded beach perfect for relaxation. There are multiple outbuildings, including an RV Carport with sewer connection. Spread across 3 lots, it offers potential for expansion or sale. The possibilities are endless!
